ammer or pepper spray (literally) a flying punk pig : that's part of your job as a master chef.\nAre you ready to slice with a knife (workshop 1), peel or block with a peeler (workshop 2), smash with a hammer (workshop 3), season or shoot with a one-of-a-kind salt mill (workshop 4) or avoid monsterish ingredients coming from a canon with your wild kitchen tools to score the top of the charts ?\n10 recipes, with 4 workshops each, are included : that's 40 ways to have crazy fun ! \nFor now it's a solo game but we are working on making it a multiplayer game. \nIt's only the beginning ! We will regularly add new features, music, recipes, new tools and new workshops. \nThank you for purchasing the game. It means the world !", "short_description": "Crazy Cook\u00ae is a fun and crazy cooking game for the whole family !\nYour goal is to create great recipes\u2026with a twist : the ingredients are a bit hostile !\nSlice a chickenosaurus, peel a smiling onion, avoid a killer tomato, smash a garlic grenade with a hammer or pepper spray (literally) a flying punk pig : that's part of your job as a master chef.\n10 recipes, with 4 workshops each, are included : that's 40 ways to have crazy fun ! \nAre you ready to score the top of the charts ?"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "661548015107496", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Crazy Cook", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Crazy Cook\u00ae est un jeu fun et un peu fou pour toute la famille ! ", "short_description": "Crazy Cook\u00ae est un jeu fun et un peu fou pour toute la famille ! \n"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "527734402268659", "locale": "en_GB", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Crazy Cook", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Crazy Cook\u00ae is a fun and crazy cooking game in VR for the whole family !\nYour goal is to create great recipes\u2026with a twist : the ingredients are a bit hostile !\nSlice a chickenosaurus, peel a smiling onion, avoid a killer tomato, smash a garlic grenade with a hammer or pepper spray (literally) a flying punk pig : that's part of your job as a master chef.\nAre you ready to slice with a knife (workshop 1), peel or block with a peeler (workshop 2), smash with a hammer (workshop 3), season or shoot with a one-of-a-kind salt mill (workshop 4) or avoid monsterish ingredients coming from a canon with your wild kitchen tools to score the top of the charts ?\nFor now it's a solo game but we are working on making it a multiplayer game. \nIt's only the beginning ! We will regularly add new recipes, new tools and new workshops. \nThank you for purchasing the game. It means the world !", "short_description": "Crazy Cook\u00ae is a fun and crazy cooking game for the whole family !\nYour goal is to create great recipes\u2026with a twist : the ingredients are a bit hostile !\nSlice a chickenosaurus, peel a smiling onion, avoid a killer tomato, smash a garlic grenade with a hammer or pepper spray (literally) a flying punk pig : that's part of your job as a master chef.\nAre you ready to slice, peel, smash, season (shoot) or avoid monsterish ingredients with your wild kitchen tools to score the top of the charts ?"}]}, "developer_name": "Jungle Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://junglegames.io/politique-de-confidentialite/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://junglegames.io/conditions-de-service-eula/", "publisher_name": "Jungle Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://junglegames.io/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "ACTION", "FOOD"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT